OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781287881
OL,3,CNine arrested in Immigration
OL,4,CEnforcement swoop at DPD bases
OL,6,FNine people have been arrested for
OL,7,Fsuspected illegal working at DPD bases
OL,8,Fin Basingstoke and Newbury.
OL,10,FImmigration Enforcement officers
OL,11,Fcarried out early morning swoops at
OL,12,Fboth sites on Thursday 11 June, in a
OL,13,Fbid to crack down on illegal working
OL,14,Fin the delivery sector.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
