PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781287881
OL,3,CNine arrested in Immigration
OL,4,CEnforcement swoop at DPD bases
OL,6,FOfficers carried out right to work
OL,7,Fchecks on over 100 people. Seven
OL,8,FIndian nationals, one Ghanaian
OL,9,Fnational and one Pakistani national
OL,10,Fwere identified as immigration
OL,11,Foffenders. Eight of the nine arrested
OL,12,Fwere at the Basingstoke site.
OL,14,FAll have been placed on immigration
OL,15,Fbail, subject to strict conditions,
OL,16,Fwhile further inquiries take place. If
OL,17,Fthey are found to have been working
OL,18,Funlawfully, they will be removed from
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
