PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781287881
OL,3,CNine arrested in Immigration
OL,4,CEnforcement swoop at DPD bases
OL,6,FAny employer found in breach of the
OL,7,Flaw can receive a fine of up to
OL,8,F#60,000 per worker.
OL,10,FThe Home Office said the operation
OL,11,Fforms part of the Home Secretary's
OL,12,Freforms to the immigration system, to
OL,13,Fscale up removals of those with no
OL,14,Fright to be in the UK and remove the
OL,15,Fincentives drawing illegal migrants to
OL,16,FBritain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
