OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781287881
OL,3,CNine arrested in Immigration
OL,4,CEnforcement swoop at DPD bases
OL,6,FSince coming into power in July 2024,
OL,7,Fit said the Government has increased
OL,8,Fillegal working enforcement activity
OL,9,Fto the highest level in British
OL,10,Fhistory, with an 83% rise in arrests
OL,11,Fand 77% increase in raids across the
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,FSouth Central Immigration Enforcement
OL,15,FLead, Adam Duffin said:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
