OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781287881
OL,3,CNine arrested in Immigration
OL,4,CEnforcement swoop at DPD bases
OL,6,F"Many weeks of preparation and
OL,7,Fintelligence building has led to this
OL,8,Fresult and work continues to ensure
OL,9,Fthat where an employer has employed an
OL,10,Findividual illegally, the liable party
OL,11,Freceives the appropriate penalty.
OL,13,F"I want this to send a message to
OL,14,Fthose firms who are attempting to
OL,15,Fflout the rules ` we are cracking down
OL,16,Fon this and we will put a stop to it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@fO]
